{
  "an1.188:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1 ",
  "an1.188:0.2": "14. Paṭhamavagga ",
  "an1.188-197:1.1": "\"Etadaggaṁ, bhikkhave, mama sāvakānaṁ bhikkhūnaṁ rattaññūnaṁ yadidaṁ aññāsikoṇḍañño.",
  "an1.188-197:1.2": "…   Mahāpaññānaṁ yadidaṁ sāriputto.",
  "an1.188-197:2.1": "",
  "an1.188-197:2.2": "…   Iddhimantānaṁ yadidaṁ mahāmoggallāno.",
  "an1.188-197:2.3": "…   Dhutavādānaṁ yadidaṁ mahākassapo.",
  "an1.188-197:2.4": "…   Dibbacakkhukānaṁ yadidaṁ anuruddho.",
  "an1.188-197:2.5": "…   Uccākulikānaṁ yadidaṁ bhaddiyo kāḷigodhāya putto.",
  "an1.188-197:2.6": "…   Mañjussarānaṁ yadidaṁ lakuṇḍaka bhaddiyo.",
  "an1.188-197:2.7": "…   Sīhanādikānaṁ yadidaṁ piṇḍolabhāradvājo.",
  "an1.188-197:2.8": "…   Dhammakathikānaṁ yadidaṁ puṇṇo mantāṇiputto.",
  "an1.188-197:2.9": "…   Saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṁ vibhajantānaṁ yadidaṁ mahākaccāno\"ti.\nVaggo paṭhamo.\nPaṭhamavagga"
}